  ${
    $d t x B $.  $d t x F $.  $d t x X $.  $d t x Y $.
    fgmin.1 $e |- X = U. B $.
    fgmin.2 $e |- Y = U. F $.
    $( Minimality property of a generated filter: every filter that contains
       ` B ` contains its generated filter. $)
    fgmin $p |- ( ( B e. fBas /\ F e. Fil /\ X = Y ) -> ( B C_ F <-> ( filGen `
    B ) C_ F ) ) $=
      ( vt vx cfbas wcel cfil wceq w3a wss cfg cfv wa cv wrex wb elfg 3ad2ant1
      adantr wi sseq2 3ad2ant3 ssrexv adantl fillsb 3expd com34 r19.23adv
      ad2antlr syld com23 3adantl3 sylbid imp3a ssrdv ex fbssfg sstr2 syl
      impbid ) AIJZBKJZCDLZMZABNZAOPZBNZVHVIVKVHVIQZGVJBVLGRZVJJZVMCNZHRZVMNZHA
